# Project Components

The network consists of three logical environments.

## Corporate Office

Provides an enterprise LAN consisting of multiple VLANs, wired and wireless connectivity, and centralized routing.

## Home Network

Represents a residential customer network with wired and wireless devices connected through a dedicated home router.

## ISP Network

Represents the external service provider responsible for connecting independent customer networks.

